gia na doulepsoun ta .py arxeia arkei na yparxoun proegkatestimena ta requirments, na yparxei ena wallet me onoma 'wallet1', to opoio dimiourgisa me to 'bitcoin-cli createwallet "wallet1" sto terminal kai na exei syndesei to bitcoin sto regtest me sygkekrimenes rythmiseis tou bitcoin.conf, gia ayto ton logo episynapw sto zip kai to bitcoin.conf, opote apla xreiazete na antikatastathei me to yparxon sto fakelo .bitcoin. apo ekei kai pera patwntas run sto kwdika tou 2.py, ayto tha treksei kanonika. Gia thn ektelesh tou programmatos xrhsimopoihsa to bitcoind, linux kai to visual studio code.
